00:00:07.942 --> 00:00:11.378 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Weather] This is strange,
illogical even.

00:00:11.411 --> 00:00:14.916 position:7% line:83% align:start
Whoever the enemy is, they're
using a Stand right now.

00:00:14.949 --> 00:00:16.751 position:24% line:83% align:start
