Come back here, body.

00:00:42.476 --> 00:00:44.946 position:16% line:83% align:start
If the enemy is smart,
they'll try to assassinate me

00:00:44.979 --> 00:00:47.447 position:21% line:83% align:start
while I'm vulnerable
without my Stand.

00:00:47.481 --> 00:00:49.984 position:30% line:83% align:start
My top priority
is protecting my body.

00:00:50.018 --> 00:00:51.485 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[Narciso gasps]
-[sirens blaring]

00:00:52.820 --> 00:00:54.154 position:13% line:89% align:start
What the hecks he doing?

