00:02:45.933 --> 00:02:48.268 position:13% line:83% align:start
Could it be because you're
not affected by its power?

00:02:49.336 --> 00:02:52.073 position:30% line:83% align:start
You can leave
finding my body to me, Weather.

00:02:52.106 --> 00:02:53.941 position:16% line:83% align:start
Just go after the enemy
Stand User!

00:02:55.643 --> 00:02:56.276 position:35% line:89% align:start
