Come out right now!

00:04:54.028 --> 00:04:55.062 position:38% line:83% align:start
[dwarf 1]
Yay! Hurray!

00:04:55.096 --> 00:04:56.531 position:38% line:83% align:start
[dwarf 2]
The Princess has awakened!

00:04:56.564 --> 00:04:59.233 position:19% line:83% align:start
