00:05:48.015 --> 00:05:49.784 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[goats bleating]
-[gasps]

00:05:53.955 --> 00:05:56.489 position:24% line:89% align:start
[bleating weakly]

00:05:57.457 --> 00:05:58.559 position:10% line:89% align:start
