for eating my brothers!

00:07:07.361 --> 00:07:10.497 position:27% line:83% align:start
Shit. Now I get
the enemy Stand's target.

00:07:10.531 --> 00:07:12.833 position:10% line:89% align:start
It was never after my body.

00:07:12.867 --> 00:07:15.503 position:33% line:83% align:start
It wanted me
to join the fantasy

00:07:15.536 --> 00:07:17.705 position:7% line:83% align:start
and I've already been dragged
into a story!

00:07:21.509 --> 00:07:22.543 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Van Gogh] Excuse me.

00:07:22.576 --> 00:07:24.045 position:27% line:83% align:start
