00:07:53.607 --> 00:07:57.078 position:19% line:83% align:start
Just last night with a
razor blade, I cut off my ear.

00:07:57.111 --> 00:07:59.213 position:30% line:89% align:start
[eerie music]

00:07:59.246 --> 00:08:00.915 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:08:00.948 --> 00:08:05.086 position:5% line:83% align:start
