00:08:21.402 --> 00:08:22.937 position:19% line:89% align:start
[breathing nervously]

00:08:25.573 --> 00:08:27.975 position:19% line:83% align:start
You want some of this,
you bitch?

00:08:28.009 --> 00:08:28.943 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:08:32.279 --> 00:08:35.750 position:27% line:83% align:start
[goat 2] Mama!
